    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and ready for all your upcoming road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great in the driveway, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
