    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a sweet new ride? I'm parting with my super reliable car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect fit for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken care of it like family, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it just as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
